<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Page not found. Oops, looks like the page you were looking for doesn’t exist.">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #FF2E63;
            font-size: 48px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #FF2E63;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #E02456;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Oops! Page Not Found.</h1>
    <p>It looks like the page you're looking for doesn’t exist. But don’t worry, you can always go back to our <a href="index.html">Home Page</a> and find what you're looking for!</p>

</body>
</html>
